metadata.name: The Origin
metadata.description:
Featuring BAYC #7676 and BAKC #3263

"I played off the Japanese headband. Put your ape and his dog launching out of a bowl at a skateboarding contest off the coast of Fukushima. I pulled a little inspiration from the MAYC decks going around with the power plant and green sludge. Hand drawn, hand inked, fonts and edges cleaned in photoshop."
